{"type": "article", "id": 26785, "title": "“最具价值品牌”揭晓，以及，给你夏季派对着装指南｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-13T10:54:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 20, "name": "汽车"}, {"id": 137, "name": "女性"}, {"id": 3883, "name": "榜单"}, {"id": 2008, "name": "指甲油"}, {"id": 319, "name": "电商"}, {"id": 15805, "name": "双肩包"}, {"id": 1856, "name": "泳衣"}, {"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}, {"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 27581, "name": "For Love & Lemons"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 27582, "name": "DS Automobiles"}, {"id": 3510, "name": "OPI"}, {"id": 111, "name": "迪士尼"}, {"id": 27583, "name": "Yoox-Net-A-Porter"}, {"id": 18258, "name": "菲拉格慕"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 93, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702121906psoxl9uXtn0ZJV75.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Salvatore-Ferragamo-appoints-former-Furla-CEO-to-lead-group,692308.html#.VzTNC4QrJQY\"><b>Furla 前 CEO 加入菲拉格慕</b></a>｜意大利奢侈品集团 Salvatore Ferragamo 宣布任命 Furla 前 CEO Eraldo Poletto 担任集团首席行政官。而此前的 CEO Michele Norsa 2006 年加入公司，刚刚过去的四月底离职。同时宣布一季度核心利润增长。一季度息税折旧摊销前利润增至 6400 万欧元（约合 7300 万美元） ，高于汤森路透 6000 万欧元的预期。而在集团最大的市场亚太地区，销售额下跌了 3%，以港澳及日本地区的疲软为主。欧洲区销售额下跌的同时，北美地区增长。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Yoox-Net-A-Porter-Q1-sales-rise-14-pct,692273.html#.VzTNDoQrJQY\"><b>Yoox-Net-A-Porter 一季度销售额增长 13.8%</b></a>｜意大利奢侈品电商集团 Yoox-Net-A-Porter 宣布一季度销售额获 13.8% 的增长，至 4.46 亿欧元，略低于预期的 4.53 亿欧元，恒定汇率下销售额增长了 14.5%。活跃用户从 220 万增至 250 万人次。<br></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/designer-luxury/organizational-changes-ralph-lauren-q4-results-stefan-larsson-fashion-apparel-luxury-designer-10429216/\"><b>新店及线上销售助 Ralph Lauren 收益胜预期</b></a>｜奢侈集团 Ralph Lauren 宣布四季度收入及利润胜预期，有赖于新门店以及线上销售份额增长。但其它各项几乎均呈下跌状态，纯收入有 0.7% 的下滑，从 18.9 亿跌至 18.7 亿美元。净批发销售额减少了 6.5% 至 9.42 亿美元，店铺净销售额上涨了 5.7% 至 8.89 亿美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/forbes-worlds-most-valuable-brands-2016\"><b>福布斯发布“世界最具价值品牌”榜单</b></a>｜福布斯（Forbes）近日发布“世界最具价值品牌”榜单，其中苹果、Google 和微软以 1541 亿美元、825 亿美元和 752 亿美元的品牌价值位居前三。4-10 位依次为可口可乐、Facebook、丰田、IBM、迪士尼、麦当劳和通用电气。名列第 5 的 Facebook 44% 的增长速度，为前 100 位中增速最快的品牌。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/OPI-partners-with-Disney-releases-Alice-Through-the-Looking-Glass-collection,692283.html#.VzUjn4QrJQY\"><b>OPI 推出迪士尼合作款甲油</b></a>｜迪士尼最近与 Marc by Marc Jacobs、丝芙兰和 Urban Decay 等彩妆进行了合作，而最新的是与 OPI 指甲油，推出了“爱丽丝梦游仙境”系列。8 种颜色组成，据说灵感来自“爱丽丝梦游仙境”的奇思妙想、梦幻、冒险等精神（但好像也看不出什么特别）。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121852YBoUFIrkjC6itGpb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.332\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">夏季的 Party 怎么穿，可以参考 <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/summer-party-dresses-hm-shop/\">H&amp;M 最新的“ Party Parade”系列</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121852px9FHTnz0u43vJoA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121853xTXvpjn0wgUH2AQc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121853q9FNRemrsbEYSP5x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121854NG1MTOXcCBlV2ZqD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121854PxYnWrkCIwm71Bc0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/DS-Automobiles-and-Givenchy-Le-MakeUp-together-for-the-new-DS3,692255.html#.VzUjqYQrJQY\">法国 DS Automobiles 汽车与纪梵希（Givenchy ）彩妆合作</a>，针对女性推出 1400 辆 DS3 车款的内外部的外观都重新设计，车内中央扶手集中放置纪梵希彩妆，每辆车内的一套特别彩妆包含睫毛膏、唇膏、粉饼和指甲油。6 月 7 日上市。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021218553NAdng9wX4HSIOh2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121855LYGaEAzX7fpPjdtQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121856CkDlqFXOSpT3uUKd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121856zIPYkFvGLHCfrmWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121857fr7Z8mCMkR5Nozqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.36018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/05/11/gucci-tropical-backpack/#slide-4\">Gucci 又推出皮质双肩背包</a>，热带印花系列：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121857MXmYUNz7kG0OlpuI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121858ONBx1IdC4n2ytRbD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121858j0H7B2NUvATc8qoX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04347826\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121859Cr9cbvwPyZFdG3V5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04347826\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>三叶草与 Pharrell Williams 合作的<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/05/12/adidas-originals-pharrell-williams-spring-summer-2016/#slide-7\"> Pink Beach 系列释出更多沙滩装</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121859rkn0euv1L4sXZtQo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72966208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121900wCxPl4cLhEJpMVAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72966208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121900fBw6aSHRIcmQ1ruq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72966208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">洛杉矶时装品牌 <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/for-love-lemons-summer-2016-collection/#jp-carousel-290594\"> For Love &amp; Lemons 推出推出夏季系列 Reverie</a>，满是花朵和蕾丝点缀的裙装，看起来很浪漫：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021219017ALaDR9g42siIJvO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121901hTw3trl5yIUm4CEg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121902EaiYdB7fjXQV31pS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121902R9Mo7hVAB05kJQxn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121903Yrl8hsO5CvRmw7aW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021219030Ysq1pz9yi3n2BA8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021219052NyuaVXH7g9PWQYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}